                "labels": [
                    {
                        "purpose": "M+ Sigg Collection",
                        "text": "This painting is part of a series in which Wang Guangyi applies abstract methods to classical western paintings. Here he borrows French painter Jacques-Louis David’s neo-classical 1793 masterpiece of the same title and flattens and subdues the rich colours of the original composition while mirroring the central figure."
                    },
                    {
                        "purpose": "Sigg Online",
                        "text": "This painting is part of a series in which Wang Guangyi applies abstract methods to Western paintings. Here he borrows French painter Jacques-Louis David’s neoclassical 1793 masterpiece The Death of Marat, flattening and subduing the rich colours of the original composition while mirroring the central figure."
                    }
                ]
            },
            "zh-hant": {
                "purposes": [
                    "M+ Sigg Collection",
                    "Sigg Online"
                ],
                "labels": [
                    {
                        "purpose": "M+ Sigg Collection",
                        "text": "這是王廣義將西方經典名畫抽象化而創作的系列畫作之一；他以法國新古典畫家雅克-路易・大衛於1793年的新古典主義的名作為藍本進行同名創作，把原作平面化，把豐富色彩轉化成單色，並將核心人物鏡像化。"
                    },
                    {
